    {
      "id": 395810,
      "category": "researcher",
      "content": "Due to a lack of sanitization in the name field of the CSMONEY newsletter registration form, it was possible to inject HTML codes, which were reflected in the confirmation email.\n\nAn attacker could insert a payload that completely modifies the visible HTML of the email, causing any victim to receive the malicious email directly from go@cs.money, facilitating phishing attacks.\n\n\n{██████████}\n{F3001233}\n\nhttps://email.cs.money/archive/csmoney_eng",
